,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2968,432,'Contracts','Advanced','Contracts require third-party service provider’s security policies meet or\nexceed those of the institution.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2969,432,'Contracts','Advanced','A third-party termination/exit strategy has been established and validated with management.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2970,432,'Ongoing Monitoring','Advanced','Third-party employee access to confidential data on third-party hosted systems is tracked actively via automated reports and alerts.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2971,433,'Planning','Intermediate','A strategy is in place to coordinate and communicate with internal and external stakeholders during or following a cyber attack.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2972,433,'Planning','Intermediate','Plans are in place to re-route or substitute critical functions and/or services that may be affected by a successful attack on Internet-facing systems.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2973,433,'Planning','Intermediate','A direct cooperative or contractual agreement(s) is in place with an incident response organization(s) or provider(s) to assist rapidly with mitigation efforts.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2974,433,'Planning','Intermediate','Lessons learned from real-life cyber incidents and attacks on the institution and other organizations are used to improve the institution’s risk mitigation capabilities and response plan.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2975,433,'Testing','Intermediate','Cyber-attack scenarios are analyzed to determine potential impact to critical business processes.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2976,433,'Testing','Intermediate','The institution participates in sector-specific cyber exercises or scenarios (e.g., FS-ISAC Cyber Attack (against) Payment Processors (CAPP)).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2977,433,'Testing','Intermediate','Resilience testing is based on analysis and identification of realistic and highly likely threats as well as new and emerging threats facing the institution.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2978,433,'Testing','Intermediate','The critical online systems and processes are tested to withstand stresses for extended periods (e.g., DDoS).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2979,433,'Testing','Intermediate','The results of cyber event exercises are used to improve the incident response plan and automated triggers.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2980,434,'Detection','Intermediate','The incident response program is triggered when anomalous behaviors and attack patterns or signatures are detected.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2981,434,'Detection','Intermediate','The institution has the ability to discover infiltration, before the attacker traverses across systems, establishes a foothold, steals information, or causes damage to data and systems.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2982,434,'Detection','Intermediate','Incidents are detected in real time through automated processes that include instant alerts to appropriate personnel who can respond.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2983,434,'Detection','Intermediate','Network and system alerts are correlated across business units to better detect and prevent multifaceted attacks (e.g., simultaneous DDoS attack and account takeover).',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2984,434,'Detection','Intermediate','Incident detection processes are capable of correlating events across the enterprise.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2985,434,'Response and Mitigation','Intermediate','Analysis of security incidents is performed in the early stages of an intrusion to minimize the impact of the incident.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2986,434,'Response and Mitigation','Intermediate','Any changes to systems/applications or to access entitlements necessary for incident management are reviewed by management for formal approval before implementation.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2987,434,'Response and Mitigation','Intermediate','Processes are in place to ensure assets affected by a security incident that cannot be returned to operational status are quarantined, removed, disposed of, and/or replaced.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2988,434,'Response and Mitigation','Intermediate','Processes are in place to ensure that restored assets are appropriately reconfigured and thoroughly tested before being placed back into operation.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39'),(2989,435,'Escalation and Reporting','Intermediate','Employees that are essential to mitigate the risk (e.g., fraud, business resilience) know their role in incident escalation.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-24 09:58:39','2019-09-24 09:58:39');

